page.content:
{Bishops Nympton School Football Team
We have recently won the six a-side football tournament at the{South {Molton Community College.}There were fourteen teams there and we played six of them.We did not have a goal scored against us.We eventually got through to the final.There we won 2-0 against{Filleigh.}Adam went to get the shield.Then the rest of the team went to collect their medals. The teams they were up against were partly teams that we had not played like{Goodliegh and Bratton Flemming. {We have played Filleigh}a number of times and beat them every time. This season we had approximately nine games.The transport is usually Adam's mum,Matthew's mum and dad, Robert Murch's mum and Robert Barons's mum. {By Adam White.
